## Home services across Srinagar

Panun Kaergar is Kashmir’s on-demand home services platform for Srinagar residents who want reliable help without chasing technicians. Book once — we handle partner assignment, scheduling, and support.

Whether you live near **Lal Chowk**, **Rajbagh**, **Hyderpora**, **Bemina**, **Hazratbal**, or farther out toward **Nowgam** and **Pantha Chowk**, tell us your locality and we confirm a verified partner nearby.

### What you can book in Srinagar

Carpentry and furniture work, plumbing and leak fixes, electrical wiring and repairs, masonry, deep cleaning, pest control, laundry & dry clean, painting, home appliance repair, gardening, men’s and women’s salon, interior décor, aluminium & steel works, vehicle services, and pet grooming.

### How booking works

1. Choose your service and share your Srinagar address or landmark.
2. Book by phone, WhatsApp, website, or the Panun Kaergar app.
3. We confirm availability and send a verified local partner.

Availability is zone-based. The app and our team confirm whether your address is serviceable before you commit.
